title: Caitlyn Jenner not ready to wear swimsuit
text:
Other Articles Miranda Lambert enjoys girls' night with Shania Twain post split Kourtney Kardashian stuns in sexy swimsuit post ex-beau's post Gisele Bundchen ridiculed for keeping 'boob job' secret under burqa Reality TV star Caitlyn Jenner has confessed that she is not ready to expose herself in a swimsuit.
In the latest episode of her docuseries, “I Am Cait” Caitlyn Jenner, 65, went on a road trip to San Francisco but when her friends stripped down in swimsuit to have a dip in a hot tub, she decided to skip it and spend time in her room, reported Aceshowbiz.
“I don’t think I’m ready for that. You have to realise these girls transitioned years and years and years ago. I just don’t know if I’m ready to expose myself like that.
“Maybe down the line I’ll feel more comfortable with myself, but right now I just can’t see myself doing it,” said Caitlyn Jenner.
The other issue, which Caitlyn spoke about was the need of making her voice feminine after her transition.
Caitlyn Jenner told her stepdaughter Kim Kardashian about considering a surgery to alter her voice.
To which Kim expressed her concern saying, “What if they made a mistake and you had no voice?”
First Published on August 03, 2015 2:34 pm
